text:
``` &lt;div class="Nav__Desktop-Menu-Items-Wrapper"&gt;
          {% for item in module.navigation_options %}
           {% if item.item_type == "dropdown" %}
          &lt;div class="Dropdown_Action Menu-Item"&gt;
            &lt;div class="dropdown dropdown-has-anchor" role="button" id="dropdown-selector"&gt;
              &lt;i class="caret down icon arrow-down" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
              &lt;div class="Nav__Desktop-Dropdown-Menu-Text"&gt;{{ item.menu_item }}&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;ul class="dropdown__menu" data-dropdown="#dropdown-selector"&gt;
                &lt;div class="popup-menu"&gt;
                 {% for item2 in item.dropdown_items %}
                  &lt;div class="popup-content-wrapper"&gt;
              &lt;a href="{{ item2.dropdown_item_link.href }}"&gt;
                &lt;img src="{{ item2.dropdown_item_icon.src }}" class="popup-image"/&gt;
                &lt;p class="Nav__Desktop-Dropdown-Menu-Item-Title"&gt;{{ item2.dropdown_title }}&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;p class="Nav__Desktop-Dropdown-Item-Subtitle"&gt;{{ item2.dropdown_description }}&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/a&gt;
                  &lt;/div&gt;
                   {% endfor %}
                &lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

          {% endif %}
          {% if item.item_type == "link" %}
          &lt;a href="{{ item.nav_item_link.href }}" class="Nav__Desktop-Dropdown-Menu-Text Nav__Desktop-Link Menu-Item"&gt;{{ item.menu_item }}&lt;/a&gt;
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
              &lt;/div&gt;```

```
.dropdown:after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 200;
    border: 0;
    border-left: 10px solid transparent;
    border-right: 10px solid transparent;
    margin-left: -10px;
    left: 40%;
    border-bottom: 10px solid #fff;
    top: 54%;
    transition: 280ms all 120ms ease-out;
    opacity: 0;
    will-change: opacity;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
}```
